body:
Hello, it's me (sorry for the meme). You may or may not be aware (many aren't) that I do photography as a hobby (just simple phone camera) and I wanted to share some of my pictures with the community and see what the response was. 

Shots (Imgur Album): http://www.imgur.com/a/jJeFp

replies.body:
There are some that need to be fixed or taken again, the rest are fine I guess.
I'd say you're over the average photographer.

replies.body:
That's actually pretty damn good looking!

I have a soft spot for photography as well :3

I like to take pictures of weird faces my mom makes

and all the people in Kaldorei will know my hairy legs and unibrow :3

LOL

But really, that's some pretty dang good pictures. Keep it up!

replies.body:
Great start! Love the one with the red pier! Also If you were to take this hobby seriously, I recommend a good camera...
also watch Casey Neistat: https://www.youtube.com/user/caseyneistat
He does vlogs everyday and he does photography and film for a living, and gives good advice for anyone who want to take this as a profession!
